          h2 MONITORING & EVALUATION
          p We have developed a monitoring and evaluation tools that would help the trainers measuring and assessing the programmes activity and results. The purpose of using our well designed tools is to check on the progress of implementation and outputs methodically. The tools record trainers perspective, what has worked well, what has not worked well, what needs to stay same and what needs to change. These tools will help us determine who is doing well among the occupants in the house and when changes may be needed.
