          h2 Core & Additional Assessment 
          p Our assessment tools accurately identify needs & risk of offenders & underprivileged. We recognize that assessment can be a daunting experience for some inmates and ex-offenders. But needs and risk assessment helps identify the person your CSR is supporting that we, (TCP) are serving. 
          p Needs and risk are used to determine the need for specialized treatment program such as antisocial behaviour, violent & aggression, substance & alcohol abuse, mental health and cognitive skill building before proceed to skills acquisition, vocational training and WAEC to higher education. 




